# Local environment files. Never commit these: this repository is public, so
# an accidental `git add -A` is immediately and irreversibly disclosed.
# A local `.git/info/exclude` entry is not sufficient — it is per-clone and is
# never committed, so it protects neither other contributors nor CI checkouts.
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

